Sankey Charts
Use a sankey chart to visualize the distribution of a measure from one grouping to another grouping.
The sankey chart performs calculations based on the absolute value of each measure.
Keep these considerations in mind when using sankey charts:
Sankey charts don't support scroll and don't render when there's not enough space.
To facet and filter dashboard widgets based on a grouping in a sankey chart, set the chartâ€™s Selection Type as Multiple Selection.
